These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
4 different games are played: billiard, domino, whist, mah-jongg
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, teacher, musician, firefighter
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, pear, pineapple, grapefruit
1. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person eating pear##1
2. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the musician##1
4. the person playing billiard is the manager##1
5. the manager is on the right of the musician##1
6. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the firefighter##1
7. the teacher is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Game    | domino  | mah-jongg | whist    | billiard       |
| Job         | teacher | firefighter    | musician      | manager |
| Food   | asparagus   | pineapple | pear | grapefruit        |

