.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
City: san-francisco, hannover, miami, london
4 different pets are kept: pony, frog, hamster, rabbit
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, dancing, drawing, writing
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
3. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is the owner of the pony##1
6. the person who's hobby is writing is the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| City        | miami   | hannover | san-francisco     | london      |
| Pet         | frog | hamster | rabbit | pony |
| Hobby   | dancing    | writing   | drawing     | baking      |

