.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
House: futuristic, colonial, cottage, palace
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, documentary, comedy
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, 7up, water, iced-tea
1. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the futuristic house##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the cottage house##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
4. the palace house is the person watching documentary movies##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking water##1
7. the futuristic house is the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| House         | futuristic | colonial | cottage | palace |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy       | drama    | crime | documentary     |
| Beverage   | milk | water    | iced-tea | 7up    |

