.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, corn, tomato, pumpkin
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, daisy, poppy, dahlia
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, old-henry, fonseca, vegafina
1. the person eating tomato is the vegafina-smoker##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is on the far left##1
3. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
4. the person eating corn is on the far right##1
5. the person who growspoppy is on the far right##1
6. the person who growsmarigold is the person eating tomato##1
7. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
8. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Food         | grapefruit | pumpkin | tomato | corn |
| Flower       | daisy     | dahlia      | marigold     | poppy      |
| Cigar   | old-henry | alhambra         | vegafina      | fonseca        |

