.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, milk, cola
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, classical, blues, ambient
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, cain, swisher, vegafina
1. the fan of classical is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
3. the cain-smoker is on the right of the fan of trance##1
4. the montecristo-smoker is the fan of blues##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
6. the person drinking 7up is the fan of classical##1
7. the person drinking cola is the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Beverage         | milk   | cola | hot-chocolate  | 7up      |
| Music-Genre   | blues  | trance        | ambient  | classical       |
| Cigar         | montecristo | swisher    | cain | vegafina |

