.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, domino, bridge, canasta
4 different pets are kept: bird, hamster, ferret, hedgehog
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, april, june, july
1. the person playing scrabble is the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left##1
5. the person playing domino is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the ferret is the person playing bridge##1
7. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
8. the person playing canasta is the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Game           | domino | bridge | canasta | scrabble |
| Pet   | hedgehog   | ferret  | hamster | bird   |
| Birthday   | july   | may     | june | april       |

