.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, begonia, tulip, amaryllis
4 different games are played: canasta, bridge, monopoly, poker
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, mauve, light-blue, blue
1. the person playing monopoly is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsbegonia is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
4. the person who likes mauve is the person who growstulip##1
5. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
6. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
7. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
8. the person playing bridge is the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Flower          | rose  | amaryllis | tulip   | begonia     |
| Game         | poker | bridge   | canasta  | monopoly |
| Color   | light-blue         | fuchsia  | mauve | blue  |

