.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, skateboarding, tennis, badminton
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, singing, writing, baking
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, fisherman, software-developer, dressmaker
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the software-developer##1
2. the dressmaker is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the software-developer##1
5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
6. the dressmaker is the person who's sport is tennis##1
7. the fisherman is on the left of the dressmaker##1
8. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Sport      | badminton | tennis     | ice-hockey | skateboarding |
| Hobby   | baking  | magic-tricks | writing       | singing    |
| Job   | fisherman   | dressmaker | freelancer    | software-developer |

