.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, fuchsia, mauve, grey
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, colombian, canadian, russian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, musical, drama, comedy
1. the colombian is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
3. the colombian is on the left of the canadian##1
4. the person watching drama movies is the person who likes fuchsia##1
5. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the russian##1
6. the russian is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
7. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Color          | mauve        | grey   | fuchsia  | light-blue   |
| Nationality   | brazilian         | russian     | colombian    | canadian       |
| Movie-Genre         | musical | superhero | drama | comedy |

