.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, monopoly, whist
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, iris, tulip, balloon-flower
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, game, pall-mall, baccarat
1. the person playing whist is the baccarat-smoker##1
2. the game-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
3. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
4. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
5. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1
6. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
7. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Game   | scrabble    | monopoly | whist | backgammon        |
| Flower       | balloon-flower | azalea  | iris | tulip     |
| Cigar        | game    | pall-mall   | baccarat  | bolivar |

