.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water, soy-milk, mirinda
There 4 different types of food: orange, cauliflower, garlic, lemon
4 different pets are kept: cat, hedgehog, bird, rat
1. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1
2. the person eating orange is on the right of the person drinking water##1
3. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
4. the person eating orange is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
5. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
6. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
7. the person eating orange is the owner of the bird##1
8. the person eating garlic is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Beverage         | iced-tea  | mirinda | water  | soy-milk |
| Food       | garlic | cauliflower        | lemon | orange       |
| Pet   | cat   | hedgehog          | rat          | bird       |

