3. the scientist is on the left of the engineer##1
4. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
5. the modern house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
6. the cape-cod house is the doctor##1
7. the scientist is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| House         | craftsman   | modern   | cape-cod | futuristic |
| City   | miami | prague | london   | new-york |
| Job   | scientist     | engineer  | doctor  | project-manager  |

