The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, begonia, orchid, bellflower
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, adventure, crime, action
1. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person who growsbegonia##1
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
4. the person who growsorchid is the person watching adventure movies##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
7. the person watching crime movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Sport           | basketball  | baseball | biathlon  | surfing |
| Flower   | orchid    | balloon-flower       | begonia | bellflower      |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | comedy  | action    | crime    |

