.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, grapes, kale, corn
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, time-travel, family, romance
4 different games are played: canasta, whist, chess, domino
1. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person eating kale##1
3. the person playing domino is on the far right##1
4. the person watching family movies is on the far right##1
5. the person watching comedy movies is the person playing chess##1
6. the person watching romance movies is on the far left##1
7. the person eating corn is on the far right##1
8. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Food           | grapes  | kale  | cauliflower | corn |
| Movie-Genre   | romance   | comedy | time-travel   | family      |
| Game         | canasta | chess    | whist   | domino         |

 